{
  "stem": "1061.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the mark, the, the x.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that if you looked at that road, you really didn't know who was who or-- and you didn't know which way the whole-- that humanity was moving.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because everything was at a standstill.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, somebody comes over and says, hey, you know, there are-- there's a Swedish Red Cross here, and they have packages, Red Cross packages for us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "First time in, in, in a-- years I've got a can of sardines.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how the Swedish Red Cross happened to be there at that time, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we only know one thing, and that is that President Roosevelt died.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my sister overhead it on the radio, while she was cleaning the office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And that was April 14.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't know anything other than that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when we found ourselves on that road that was so clogged with everybody, and, and, and nobody knew who was who and what was happening, and planes were flying over, and-- among the girls, the women, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we worked with, you know, the girls who were serving the Germans, who also carried those bags for the Germans, as I did, the personal maids, was one woman, Halina.",
      "word_count": 72
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she, she had an idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we separated ourselves from these German women whom we served-- if she-- she spoke German very well-- if she got dressed in one of the uniforms out of the rucksack that she carried or I carried or whoever carried, the maids-- if we separated ourselves, she could impersonate a German woman and say that we just got lost, 12 of us, we just got-- you know.",
      "word_count": 67
    }
  ],
